#here is some basic commands and code for setup project in typescript

npm init -y
tsc --init
npm i inquirer
npm i -D @types/inquirer


Make a file of index.ts


Then go tscofig file
-> "target": "ES2022", 
-> "module": "NodeNext",
-> "moduleResolution": "NodeNext",



Go to package.json
-> "type": "module",
-> "start": "tsc && node index.js"